text: The eleventh cycle of Holland's Next Top Model premiered on 3 September 2018 on RTL5. Anna Nooshin is again the show's host. The panel of judges was again composed of cycle 2 winner Kim Feenstra, photographer Nigel Barker and stylist JeanPaul Paula. The prizes for this cycle included a modelling contract with VDM Model Management, a fashion spread in Elle magazine, and a campaign for Colgate Max White.
